According to Apple CEO Tim Cook, the iPhone 11 was the best-selling iPhone model every week during last quarter, beating out the iPhone 11 Pro and the lower-priced iPhone XR.
.
In fact, Cook said that the three newest iPhones were the three most popular iPhones every week during the quarter.
.
